<p><em>*including Greenland</em></p>
<p><em>Croatia, Italy, Serbia, Sri Lanka  and Ukraine are in process of acceding to the Convention.</em></p>
<p><em>The IAAO, an unincorporated organisation, now comprises more than 60 members from over 40 countries.  Not all members of the IAAO are members of the Convention.</em></p>


							</div>
					</div>
				</article>
            </div>
        </section>
        
